When you think of tigers or other large cats, cute high-pitched sounds  are certainly not  what you would expect to hear — right? Meet eight-month-old tiger Sherhan, who was filmed at a Russian zoo called Forest Fairytale. The sweet sound  Sherhan makes while communicating with his mother has captured the hearts of visitors – definitely a far cry from the intimidating roar usually heard from these big cats. Sherhan is one of four tigers born  at the zoo in June 2020. TimesLIVE